# Logging Middleware

This project is a middleware logger built in Node.js for URL shortening routes. It logs each request to the evaluation server using provided credentials.

## Project Structure

Logging Middleware/ ├── routes/ ├── middleware/ ├── utils/ ├── screenshots/ ├── package.json ├── README.md


## How to Run

```bash
npm install
node index.js
API Endpoints
POST /shorturls → Shortens a URL
GET /:code → Redirects to original
GET /shorturls/:code → Get stats (clicks etc)
Logging
Middleware logs each request automatically
Custom Log() utility used for logging errors